        "text": "Glossary\nSelect the glossary term and do ⌘-F to see the glossary definition on top of the screen. Glossary terms do not look different from other text since the expectation is that you might want to Find other occurrences of the text to better understand it, and if there is a glossary definition that becomes a bonus to help you understand what is meant by the text. If you like, you can also hit g to see all the Glossary terms in the document. Try it yourself, the word ‘glossary’ has a glossary definition in this document.\nInstant Search, Reference Lookup & Translate (with Liquid)\nSelect any text and use the custom keyboard shortcut to use ‘Liquid’ to instantly search based on the text & more. To see how it works, and to download, go to: www.augmentedtext.info"
